org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model

Interface ButtonComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, GenericComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ButtonComponentImpl

    public interface ButtonComponent
extends GenericComponent
    A representation of the model object 'Button Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Format
    • Value
    • Read Descriptor
    • Write Descriptor
    • Active
    • Attribute
    • Text Height

    See Also:
    DetailViewPackage.getButtonComponent()
